description: Som kund vill jag kunna skicka pengar till andras konton. Men endast en viss mängd

elements.name: Skicka pengar till någon annans konto

steps.name: that I visit the bank site
I should log into my account
that I press Överföringar andra konton
that I enter amount of money that are less than my max transfer amount
that I enter Test as a message
I should be able to see my transaktion
I should log into the recipents account
that I press the Start button
I should be able to see the recipents transaktion
